  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/kernel\/iocdmedia\/1811412-readisrc\ncrawled: 2025-12-11T21:27:33Z\n---\n\n# readISRC\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nvirtual IOReturn readISRC(\n UInt8track,\n CDISRCisrc); \n```\n\n## Parameters\n\n- **track**: Track number from which to read the ISRC.\n- **isrc**: Buffer for the ISRC data. Buffer contents will be zero-terminated.\n\n## Return Value\n\nReturns the status of the operation.\n\n## Overview\n\nRead the International Standard Recording Code for the specified track.\n\n## Miscellaneous\n\n- **getSpeed**\n- **getTOC**\n- **read**\n- **readCD()**\n- **readCD()**\n- **readDiscInfo**\n- **readMCN**\n- **readTOC**\n- **readTrackInfo**\n- **setSpeed**\n\n",
